#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.recarray.flatten:2
msgid "Return a copy of the array collapsed into one dimension."
msgstr "傳回一個壓縮成一維數組的副本。"

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.recarray.flatten:0
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "參數"

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.recarray.flatten:16
msgid "**order**"
msgstr "**命令**"

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.recarray.flatten:-1
msgid "{'C', 'F', 'A', 'K'}, optional"
msgstr "{'C', 'F', 'A', 'K'}，可選"

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.recarray.flatten:8
msgid ""
"'C' means to flatten in row-major (C-style) order. 'F' means to flatten in "
"column-major (Fortran- style) order. 'A' means to flatten in column-major "
"order if `a` is Fortran *contiguous* in memory, row-major order otherwise. "
"'K' means to flatten `a` in the order the elements occur in memory. The "
"default is 'C'."
msgstr ""
"'C' 表示以行優先（C 風格）順序展開。 'F' 表示以列優先（Fortran 風格）順序展"
"開。 'A' 表示如果 `a' 在記憶體中是 Fortran 連續的，則按列優先順序展開；否則按"
"行優先順序展開。 'K' 表示以元素在記憶體中出現的順序展開 `a'。預設值為 'C'。"

